{"tid":1654432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最近中共開始過份了","createTime":"2019-10-14T15:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T15:30:05.000Z","uid":140831,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51c3adc768a06763db5cd1f8b4f771884a6bb345","tid":1654432,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"1967年，共產黨搞文革，美國提防。<br />\n1989年，中共屠殺大學生，美國對中共禁售武器。<br />\n2008年，中共鎮壓西藏，美國杯葛京奧開幕禮。<br />\n2016年，中共被爆活摘器官，美國通過法案保護法輪功學員及異見人士。<br />\n2019年，中共屠殺香港人，美國準備通過人權法展開全面反擊。<br />\n2020年，WW3爆發，全球各地反對中共邪惡軸心， 英國人說：「脫鈎了，是時候跟中共簽自由貿易協定了」"},{"pid":"61c97930572ea03913e2a81d77602a114ed96adc","tid":1654432,"uid":108512,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"Please use English"},{"pid":"9d82b2611da6cf466b4f6ed8befd822a9cb982a0","tid":1654432,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"61c97930572ea03913e2a81d77602a114ed96adc","tid":1654432,"uid":108512,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"Please use English"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"Why"},{"pid":"377a77a6d173b775f6bcb8877ddaaccebf0e45f5","tid":1654432,"uid":1142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d82b2611da6cf466b4f6ed8befd822a9cb982a0","tid":1654432,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"61c97930572ea03913e2a81d77602a114ed96adc","tid":1654432,"uid":108512,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"Please use English"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"Why"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:53:33.000Z","msg":"文宣"},{"pid":"4cfb9d22ece8e312e909927022c2c714e15d089d","tid":1654432,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c4f2eb4e280f69cc4ac600fb71f9895a5c0b6d32","tid":1654432,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"377a77a6d173b775